Cost-Effectiveness of Surgical Weight-Loss Interventions for Patients With Knee 
Osteoarthritis and Class III Obesity.

Kostic AM(1), Leifer VP(1), Gong Y(2), Robinson MK(3), Collins JE(3), Neogi 
T(4), Messier SP(5), Hunter DJ(6), Selzer F(3), Suter LG(7), Katz JN(8), Losina 
E(9).

Author information:
(1)Brigham and Women's Hospital, Boston, Massachusetts.
(2)Brigham and Women's Hospital, Boston, Massachusetts, and Carle Illinois 
College of Medicine, Champaign.
(3)Brigham and Women's Hospital and Harvard Medical School, Boston, 
