Carvedilol reduces the risk of decompensation and mortality in patients with 
compensated cirrhosis in a competing-risk meta-analysis.

Villanueva C(1), Torres F(2), Sarin SK(3), Shah HA(4), Tripathi D(5), Brujats 
A(6), Rodrigues SG(7), Bhardwaj A(8), Azam Z(9), Hayes PC(10), Jindal A(3), Abid 
S(4), Alvarado E(11), Bosch J(12); Carvedilol-IPD-MA-group and the Baveno 
